ygData.messageBody:
I have to say both yes and no to that one. My
main play server is Brell, where my highest Chars are
46, 29, 28, 26 (and a few lower ones). I also play on
The Seventh Hammer, my highest char being level 29.
Veeshan - level 12. And last but not least, I play on one
of the PvP-team servers. I have to say that all in
all the [older] players on the PvP-team server are
far more mature than the non-PvP(team) servers. The
Seventh Hammer has alot of younger players since it's a
newer server (than Brell) but the attitude of the
players is generally the same. You have your jerks, you
have the good people as well. The nicest server I've
ever been to tho was the test server believe it or
not. The people there, that have been around since the
begining are mostly a nice group. Easy to talk to, and
pretty friendly. Anyway, that's just my two cents. If
anything, I'll always tell ya Brell Sucks, but in all
actuality I feel the same about it that I do about the
other servers. They suck equally LoL
